This release adds the following features, updates, and fixes:
• Updated list of Wine versions.
• Updated list of dxvk and vkd3d versions.
• Updated libraries in StartWine runtime.
• Updated default prefix backup.
• Updated prefix configurations.
• Updated locales.
• Updated winetricks dll list.

• Fixed helper functions in sw_runlib.
• Fixed functions uninstaller StartWine-Launcher.
• Fixed the problem of loading game images related to blocking resources.
• Fixed incorrect detection of some hotkeys when changing the keyboard layout.
• Fixed incorrect termination of processes when the connection was lost while downloading files.

• Libraries and drivers in the container have been updated.
• Authorization and game libraries of GOG.COM and Epic Games Store services are integrated into the StartWine interface.

• Added virtual keyboard for gamepad.
• Added several animations for the interface.
• Added color scheme sample "Darkside".
• Added the StartWine RU repository for downloading and installing.
• Added automatic selection of a quick repository for downloading and installing StartWine.
• Added Wine Proton EM.
• Added StartWine Uninstaller.
• Added WOW64 subsystem for better compability with 32 bit applications.
• Added NTSYNC option for better perfomance.
• Added Wine WAYLAND driver option to run using pure Wayland.
• Added Lossless Scaling algorithm for frame generation.
• Added HDR If the game supports HDR, the switch in the game will be unlocked.
• Added automatic download function from the fastest server.
• Added StartWine build system from source code.
• Portuguese localization has been added.

• The GOG.COM game library is integrated into the StartWine interface.
• The Epic Games Store game library is integrated into the StartWine interface.
• The backup update period has been added to the settings.

• Hotkeys list are grouped by category.
• Moved some configuration files to the cache directory to save user settings after an update StartWine.
• All paths in the code are unified.
• Some of the code has been rewritten in Rust.

StartWineShell:
• Added color schemes for the interface.
• Added highlighting of exe files.
• Added the ability to load Wine when starting the game.
• Added the ability to launch GOG and Epic games installed via StartWine.
• Added environment variable SW_EDITOR to set the default text editor.

